node.text:
Introducing the @jeffreestarcosmetics #StarRanch Palette and accessories! 🐴 Inspired by my love of Wyoming and new ranch in the beautiful outskirts of Casper, this palette is my version of western and the gorgeous nature that surrounds me every day 🤎 

Launching THIS Friday Sep. 3rd @ 10AM PST / 11AM MST / 1PM EST ⛰
✨ #StarRanch Mini Palette - $28.00
🦬 Ranch Skull Mirrors - $30.00
💖 #Yak Pink Plushie - $30.00

Video by: @kamillanichole & @romansofia_ 
Makeup by: @boomkackmua & @manuelcastanotx 
Hair by: @hair_by_jay1 
Models: @tiffanykeller & @kaavikiwi 
Horses provided by: The Hat Six Ranch
Yaks from @staryakranch 🐄 

#jeffreestarcosmetics #yaks #wyoming #jeffreestar #staryaks #whiteyak

node.title: STAR RANCH by Jeffree Star Cosmetics 🤠⭐️

node.text:
Everything launches THIS Friday, July 9th @ 10am PST / 1PM EST 💛💙

Premium, Deluxe & Supreme ALL have the NEW, unreleased, #StarRanch Palette amoung other new items. 💫

Mini (Teal) – $25 ($64 Value) 
Premium  (Blue) – $60 ($115 Value) 
Deluxe (Yellow)  – $100  ($183 Value) 
Supreme (Coral) – $180 ($323 Value) 

Fashion & Accessories
Summer Tie Dye Hoodie - $55
Summer Tie Dye Crop Hoodie - $50
Summer Tie Dye Cut off Tank - $30
Summer Tie Dye Lounge Shorts - $35
Summer Tie Dye Soft Touch Hand Mirror - $25
Neapolitan Hand Mirror - $30
Tropical Pop Hand Mirror - $30
Beach Ball - $10

🌞 This years Summer Mystery Boxes are bigger than ever. Featuring new Items that are being released first to Mystery Box customers, exclusive Items, and you could also be the winner of limited-edition prizes in our first ever Jeffree Star Pink Ticket Giveaway! There are two ways to win (1) Find a Pink ticket in your Summer Mystery Box (2) Be randomly selected by subscribing to our mailing list on the giveaway tab at Jeffreestarcosmetics.com (free to enter)

#jeffreestarcosmetics #mysterybox

node.title: Jeffree Star Cosmetics 🔥 Summer Mystery Box Reveal

node.text: ⭐️ Introducing… The LED @jeffreestarcosmetics Star Makeup Mirror! Launching 8/20/2021!!! @ 10AM PST💡 It was time to turn my iconic hand mirrors into real beauty lights! 💖 Coming in 2 colors, these are touch sensitive w brightness level settings, 360° magnetic joint to allow a variety of positioning and detaches for storage and easy travel! ⭐️ Built-in Qi wireless charging pad 💫 5X magnification mirror that attaches to back on mirror 🪞 Retail: $98.00 ✨ This project was so fun to work on and make come to life! I wanted to have technological aspects while also being easy to use! 🌸 #jeffreestarcosmetics #starmirror #jeffreestar

node.text: It’s been magical to spend so much time at the @StarYakRanch 🌼 Juggling the ranch life and being a makeup mogul has been amazing, fulfilling and challenging. I flew to Idaho Falls yesterday to one of my makeup labs and we worked & filmed the development of #JeffreeStarSkin and also got to watch and film them filling and assembling the @jeffreestarcosmetics #FuckProof mascara!!! We should be able to have a FULL restock in less than three weeks ⭐️ I can’t wait for you all to see what the rest of the year has coming… 😇 #jeffreestarcosmetics #staryakranch #yak #jeffreestar #yaks #whiteyak #casperwyoming #wyoming

node.text:
THE HOLY SPIRIT OF BEAUTY 🕊💕

This collection means so much to me. Besides being the celebration for my love & obsession with the color pink, this was also created months ago during what I’ll call a “rebirth” and an awakening after a creative slump in a industry I didn’t feel like I fit in anymore. After a lot of soul searching and self reflection, I found myself again. This is Pink Religion. Thank you for coming along for the journey 💖
